state. The terms and conditions to avail Haryana Labour CM Social Security Scheme are as follows:-The worker must be registered and must be resident of Haryana.Copy of First Information Report (FIR) of Accident.Postmortem Report.Death Certificate.Recommendation Report of the concerned officer.Certificate of Legal Family Member / Dependent of Labourer.Haryana Labour Department Social Security Scheme for Labourers EligibilityAll the candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria of Mukhyamantri Samajik Suraksha Yojana to avail scheme benefits as mentioned in the table below:-Eligibility CriteriaMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09370Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e1Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoAll the candidates can avail assistance of Rs. 5 lakh in case of death of the labourers at the worksite.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}